  "title": "Facilities Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Organizing & supervising Facilities Management Service\nProviders team to ensure preventative maintenance, pest control, cleaning service, horticulture, security management</li><li>Making sure all systems are always in serviceable & operational condition</li><li>Attending to any breakdown & managing closure & incidents</li><li>Reviewing equipment design & providing guidance & input in facilities</li><li>Conducting analysis for reported breakdowns and faults to determine their cause for the prevention of future occurrences</li><li>Engaging with all external stakeholders to acquire required licenses</li><li>Implementing & maintaining research & development’s sop</li><li>Managing resources & facilities and processes to ensuring running operation</li><li>Performing routine checks and scheduled preventive maintenance of key installations such as uninterrupted power supply and electrical panels</li><li>Priority on safety 1st  and executing necessary risk assessments</li></ul><p>Working location: Buona Vista</p><p>Monday to Friday, Office hours</p>",
